column5: We had an amazing turn out for our 5th Annual Fishmaster Ultimate Charters Bait and Tackle Channel Cat Derby on the Lower Grand with 90 anglers buying tickets it put the prize money at $1800.00.  Thanks to everyone who participated, it was a great year for these monster cats!  Winners are as follows  1st Place $ 1080.00 Ben Ebeling  21.62 lbs    2nd Place $ 540.00 Lucas Draczs 21.32 lbs    3rd Place $ 180.00 Tim Ballantyne 20.64 lbs
I'm glad you announced that FM!!!
nice looking fish  I just got to get down that way and give it a try some time
What are you waiting for "T"???  ... we aint getting any younger yanno!

key, I made it too kawartha walleye opener temagami in the winter  the niagra river muskie closer in dec the BOQ fall walleye fishing and many more what I am trying to say is so many lakes so little time...LOL but I will try to squeeze it in

Not to much difference in weight from the top 3 spots in the tourny, I got to get out to this area if catfish this big are coming out of this system.  Thanks for the little report, didn't know there were catfish tournament's out there.     Mike
Wow, those are some big cats.    WAnt to make it down to Dunnville soon.  Dirk....
Congratulations to all winners    Heavyweights Thanks Fishmaster for sharing!!! Leechman
